[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **The target runs PHP 7.4.33**, which is newer than the patched versions     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m (7.1.33, 7.2.24, 7.3.11), suggesting the vulnerability may be patched.       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m However, manual testing is still recommended because:                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
