[32m│[0m differently                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **Custom PHP builds** - May have different patch levels                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Defense in depth** - Verification is always recommended                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Manual Testing Possible with Available Tools                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ✅ **YES, manual testing is feasible** using:                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **curl** - Can craft the specific malicious requests needed:                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Send requests with crafted PATH_INFO containing `%0a` (newline)            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Test `fastcgi_split_path_info` misconfigurations                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Modify FPM parameters via environment variables                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
